  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Receiving temporary ostomy because of colorectal cancer at least 3 months ago;

          -  Age of≥18 and ≤80

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Not willing or incapable to comply with all study visits and assessments

          -  Evidence of any other disease, metabolic dysfunction, physical examination finding or
             laboratory finding giving reasonable suspicion of a disease or condition that puts the
             patient at high risk for treatment-related complications
      </textblock>
